text: Ceutorhynchus is a genus of true weevils in the tribe Ceutorhynchini. There are at least 400 described species in Ceutorhynchus. Ceutorhynchus succinus Legalov, 2013 is a species from the Eocene of Europe found in Baltic amber.New and little known weevils (Coleoptera: Curculionoidea) from the Paleogene and Neogene. Andrei A.
